VL (3,2,1/6) ONE-LOOP SHIFTS
----------------------------------------------------------------------

  Convention                        Db_1         Db_2         Db_3
  ------------------------  ------------ ------------ ------------
  A: Weyl (one Weyl)                1/15            1          2/3
